{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC08_HAR_090.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Well, it's certainly nice to come look at an actual site once in a while."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "In any case, this ruin is magnificent. Having everything to be made of glass..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "It has exceeded my expectations!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x21b,
            "name_id": 0x32,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Master, please watch your step.<CR>It's very slippery."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x24,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "There's no need to worry. I have no history of slipping or falling."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh...Ayesha, did you come to explore this place, too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I came to look for materials.<CR>Mr. Harry, are you...exploring?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Mmhm! I'm a busy man, so I can't come out here too often, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I have to do a firsthand investigation every once in a while. It's my duty as a treasure seeker."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "To write another book, I figured that I had to visit this place at least once."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I see. It does seem like you'd need to examine a lot of things before you can write a book..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Mmhm. Plus, exposing my body to an ancient ruin might give me some good ideas."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Well, it might be accurate to say that I came here to work up a concept."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I-I see. Well, I know there's something amazing further down from here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "It's a forge made out of glass. It's still burning red-hot, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure it'll be helpful for your research, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "After years and years, a forge that continues to burn... That is pretty interesting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Right? It's in the depths of the ruin, so it takes a while to walk there, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Huh...? In the depths...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Yes. It's pretty far down, so there are a few dark and dangerous places along the way, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "You might be able to figure out why the forge is even there..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I should definitely take a look at it next time!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Next time?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Yes, next time. I'll come back and investigate that forge!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "And it is absolutely not because I'm afraid of going any deeper."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x56,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Now, if you'll excuse me, I must be going now, hahahaha..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Huh? But you don't need to rush back..."
        }
    ]
}